SysManage is a comprehensive centralized system management server with a
modern web-based interface.  It accepts WebSocket registrations from
SysManage agents deployed across an infrastructure and provides:

  * Agent management and monitoring
  * System metrics and health dashboards
  * Comprehensive reporting with PDF generation
  * JWT-based authentication with optional mTLS
  * Multi-user management with RBAC
  * Package inventory + update orchestration
  * Certificate, firewall, and antivirus integration
  * Real-time WebSocket communication
  * Declarative deployment plans via the SysManage agent

The server runs as an rc.d service backed by PostgreSQL and is fronted
by nginx for both the React UI and the FastAPI backend.
